<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>生楠公寓住客守则</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4457426&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607009049" alt="Enflowerz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4457426)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;">Enflowerz</a></span>创作</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/fei-hua-zhai">阅读作者的更多作品</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+193</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
